Defendant in custody.
On count 1, the defendant is sentenced to the Wisconsin State Prison System for a total of three (3) years. That is twelve (12) months IC followed by two (2) years extended supervision.
On count 2, the defendant is sentenced to the Wisconsin State Prison System for a total of three (3) years.  That is twelve (12) months IC followed by two (2) years extended supervision, consecutive to count 1.
On count 3, the defendant is sentenced to the Wisconsin State Prison System for a total of three (3) years.  That is twelve (12) months initial confinement followed by two (2) years extended supervision, concurrent with counts 1 and 2.
On count 4, the defendant is sentenced to the Wisconsin State Prison System for a total of three (3) years.  That is twelve (12) months initial confinement followed by two (2) years extended supervision, concurrent with counts 1, 2 and 3.  
The defendant is not eligible for the Challenge Incarceration Program or the Substance Abuse Program.
Conditions of extended supervision:
1) Maintain absolute sobriety;
2) No contact with T.A.N., the victim;
3) No contact with individuals under the age of 18 without agents permission;
4) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
5) Comply with sex offender registry requirements;
6) Pay court costs;
7) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
The defendant has credit for 250 days on count 1, 3 and 4 per the court.
Minutes.

Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for three (3) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) maintain absolute sobriety;
2) provide DNA sample and pay the surcharge;
3) no contact with T.A.N., the victim;
4) no contact with individuals under the age of 18 without agent's permission;
5) assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
6) comply with sex offender registry requirements;
7) pay court costs;
8) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Defendant has credit for 3 days if revoked.
